LayoutCountButton-True:
QRadioButton{color: #000000}
QRadioButton::indicator{border: 3px solid #000000; border-radius: 12px; background-color: #FFFFFF; width: 18px; height: 18px; margin-left: 5px; margin-right: 5px}
QRadioButton::indicator::checked{border: 8px solid #61136E; width: 8px; height: 8px}

QCheckBox-True:
QCheckBox{spacing: 10px; color: #000000}
QCheckBox::indicator{border: 3px solid #000000; border-radius: 6px; background-color: #FFFFFF; width: 20px; height: 20px}
QCheckBox::indicator:checked{image: url(checkmark.png)}

QRadioButton-True:
QRadioButton{color: #000000}
QRadioButton::indicator{border: 3px solid #000000; border-radius: 15px; background-color: #FFFFFF; width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-left: 5px; margin-right: 5px}
QRadioButton::indicator::checked{border: 10px solid #61136E; width: 10px; height: 10px}
